<module>
    <h>rud</h>
    <p><g>rud</g>
        <en>a thing</en> is a masculine <a href="?xx=nouns/simple_common_nouns">simple common
            noun</a>.</p>

    <p>Examples of <g>rud</g> as the subject of the predicative verb <a href="?gd=bi"><g>bi</g></a>
        – <ul>
            <li>non-specified – <ul>
                    <li>modified – <g>rud sam bith</g> <en>something, anything</en> – <xl>
                            <li>
                                <gd>A bheil rud sam bith anns a’ bhotul? Tha. Dé tha anns a’ bhotul?
                                    Tha bainne anns a’ bhotul.</gd>
                                <tr>Is there anything in the bottle? Yes, there is. What is in the
                                    bottle? There is milk in the bottle.</tr>
                                <ref text="617">td. 20</ref>
                            </li>
                        </xl>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </p>

